trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" /> objects that are stored as key/value pairs.
trans-unit.target: 키/값 쌍으로 저장된 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" /> 개체의 컬렉션을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: Each element in an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract> is a key/value pair that is stored in a <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry> object.
trans-unit.target: 각 요소에는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract> 에 저장 된 키/값 쌍을 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Each key/value pair must have a unique key.
trans-unit.target: 각 키/값 쌍은 고유 키를 있어야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract> interface enables the contained keys and values to be enumerated, but it does not imply any particular sort order.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract> 인터페이스를 사용 하는 포함 된 키와 값을 열거할 수 있지만 특정 정렬 순서를 의미 하지는 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" /> to use as the key of the element to add.
The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" /> to use as the value of the element to add.
Adds an element with a specified key and value to the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 키와 값을 갖는 요소를 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />에 추가합니다.

trans-unit.source: An element with the same key already exists in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: 같은 키를 가진 요소가 이미 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />에 있는 경우

trans-unit.source: Removes all elements from the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
The key to locate in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
Indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> contains an element with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 키를 갖는 요소가 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />에 들어 있는지 여부를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> contains an element with the specified key; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" />에 지정한 키가 있는 요소가 포함되어 있으면 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract" /> that can be used to iterate through the elements in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract" />의 요소를 반복하는 데 사용할 수 있는 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract" /> that can be used to iterate through the elements in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract" />의 요소를 반복하는 데 사용할 수 있는 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 열거자를 사용하여 컬렉션의 데이터를 읽을 수는 있지만 내부 컬렉션을 수정할 수는 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: The key of the value to return.
Returns the value of the element with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 키를 갖는 요소의 값을 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" /> with the specified key.

Returns an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentCollectionContract" /> that contains the keys of the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> object.

An <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentCollectionContract" /> that contains the keys of the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> object.

Returns an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentCollectionContract" /> that contains the values of the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> object.

An <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentCollectionContract" /> that contains the values of the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> object.
The key of the element to remove.
Removes the element with the specified key from the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
<see langword="true" /> if the element is successfully found and removed; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 요소를 성공적으로 찾아서 제거한 경우 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: This method returns <see langword="false" /> if <paramref name="key" /> is not found in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드는 <paramref name="key" />가 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />에 없는 경우 <see langword="false" />을 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: The key of the value to replace.
The new value of the specified element.
Replaces the value of an element.
